<h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 36px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Applications</h1>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Applications are objects that govern the overall structure and lifecycle of Yii application systems. Each Yii application system contains a single application object which is created in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-entry-scripts.html">entry script</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and is globally accessible through the expression<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">\Yii::$app</code>.</p>
<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: #eeeeee; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;">Info: Depending on the context, when we say "an application", it can mean either an application object or an application system.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">There are two types of applications:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-web-application.html">Web applications</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-console-application.html">console applications</a>. As the names indicate, the former mainly handles Web requests while the latter console command requests.</p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 30px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Application Configurations<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="application-configurations"></a></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">When an<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-entry-scripts.html">entry script</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>creates an application, it will load a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html">configuration</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and apply it to the application, like the following:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">require(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">__DIR__&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'/../vendor/autoload.php'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">);<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />require(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">__DIR__&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'/../vendor/yiisoft/yii2/Yii.php'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">);<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;load&nbsp;application&nbsp;configuration<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$config&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;require(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">__DIR__&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'/../config/web.php'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">);<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;instantiate&nbsp;and&nbsp;configure&nbsp;the&nbsp;application<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">(new&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">web</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Application</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$config</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">))-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">run</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">();</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Like normal<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html">configurations</a>, application configurations specify how to initialize properties of application objects. Because application configurations are often very complex, they usually are kept in<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html#configuration-files">configuration files</a>, like the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">web.php</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>file in the above example.</p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 30px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Application Properties<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="application-properties"></a></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">There are many important application properties that you should configure in application configurations. These properties typically describe the environment that applications are running in. For example, applications need to know how to load<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html">controllers</a>, where to store temporary files, etc. In the following, we will summarize these properties.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Required Properties<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="required-properties"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">In any application, you should at least configure two properties:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$id-detail">id</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$basePath-detail">basePath</a>.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$id-detail">id</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="id"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$id-detail">id</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property specifies a unique ID that differentiates an application from others. It is mainly used programmatically. Although not a requirement, for best interoperability it is recommended that you use alphanumeric characters only when specifying an application ID.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$basePath-detail">basePath</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="basePath"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$basePath-detail">basePath</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property specifies the root directory of an application. It is the directory that contains all protected source code of an application system. Under this directory, you normally will see sub-directories such as<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">models</code>,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">views</code>,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">controllers</code>, which contain source code corresponding to the MVC pattern.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You may configure the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$basePath-detail">basePath</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property using a directory path or a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-aliases.html">path alias</a>. In both forms, the corresponding directory must exist, or an exception will be thrown. The path will be normalized by calling the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">realpath()</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>function.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$basePath-detail">basePath</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property is often used to derive other important paths (e.g. the runtime path). For this reason, a path alias named<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@app</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>is predefined to represent this path. Derived paths may then be formed using this alias (e.g.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@app/runtime</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to refer to the runtime directory).</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Important Properties<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="important-properties"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The properties described in this subsection often need to be configured because they differ across different applications.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$aliases-detail">aliases</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="aliases"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property allows you to define a set of<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-aliases.html">aliases</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>in terms of an array. The array keys are alias names, and the array values are the corresponding path definitions. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'aliases'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'@name1'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'path/to/path1'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'@name2'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'path/to/path2'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property is provided such that you can define aliases in terms of application configurations instead of the method calls<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-baseyii.html#setAlias()-detail">Yii::setAlias()</a>.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#bootstrap()-detail">bootstrap</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="bootstrap"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This is a very useful property. It allows you to specify an array of components that should be run during the application<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#bootstrap()-detail">bootstrapping process</a>. For example, if you want a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-modules.html">module</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to customize the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-runtime-url-handling.html">URL rules</a>, you may list its ID as an element in this property.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Each component listed in this property may be specified in one of the following formats:</p>
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">an application component ID as specified via<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#components">components</a>.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">a module ID as specified via<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#modules">modules</a>.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">a class name.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">a configuration array.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">an anonymous function that creates and returns a component.</li>
</ul>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'bootstrap'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;an&nbsp;application&nbsp;component&nbsp;ID&nbsp;or&nbsp;module&nbsp;ID<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'demo'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;a&nbsp;class&nbsp;name<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\components\Profiler'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;a&nbsp;configuration&nbsp;array<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'class'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\components\Profiler'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'level'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">3</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;an&nbsp;anonymous&nbsp;function<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">function&nbsp;()&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;new&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">components</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Profiler</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">();<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: #eeeeee; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;">Info: If a module ID is the same as an application component ID, the application component will be used during the bootstrapping process. If you want to use the module instead, you may specify it using an anonymous function like the following: &gt;<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">`</code>php [</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background: #f5faff;"><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">function () {
    return Yii::$app-&gt;getModule('user');
},
</code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;">]<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">`</code></p>
</blockquote>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">During the bootstrapping process, each component will be instantiated. If the component class implements<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-bootstrapinterface.html">yii\base\BootstrapInterface</a>, its<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-bootstrapinterface.html#bootstrap()-detail">bootstrap()</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>method will also be called.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Another practical example is in the application configuration for the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-start-installation.html">Basic Application Template</a>, where the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">debug</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">gii</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>modules are configured as bootstrapping components when the application is running in development environment,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">if&nbsp;(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">YII_ENV_DEV</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">)&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;configuration&nbsp;adjustments&nbsp;for&nbsp;'dev'&nbsp;environment<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$config</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'bootstrap'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">][]&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'debug'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$config</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'modules'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">][</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'debug'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">]&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'yii\debug\Module'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$config</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'bootstrap'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">][]&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'gii'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$config</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'modules'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">][</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'gii'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">]&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'yii\gii\Module'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />}</span></code></pre>
<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: #eeeeee; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;">Note: Putting too many components in<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">bootstrap</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>will degrade the performance of your application because for each request, the same set of components need to be run. So use bootstrapping components judiciously.</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-web-application.html#$catchAll-detail">catchAll</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="catchAll"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property is supported by<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-web-application.html">Web applications</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>only. It specifies a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html">controller action</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>which should handle all user requests. This is mainly used when the application is in maintenance mode and needs to handle all incoming requests via a single action.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The configuration is an array whose first element specifies the route of the action. The rest of the array elements (key-value pairs) specify the parameters to be bound to the action. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'catchAll'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'offline/notice'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'param1'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'value1'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'param2'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'value2'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$components-detail">components</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="components"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This is the single most important property. It allows you to register a list of named components called<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-#structure-application-components.html">application components</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>that you can use in other places. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'components'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'cache'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'class'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'yii\caching\FileCache'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'user'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'identityClass'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\models\User'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'enableAutoLogin'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">true</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Each application component is specified as a key-value pair in the array. The key represents the component ID, while the value represents the component class name or<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html">configuration</a>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You can register any component with an application, and the component can later be accessed globally using the expression<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">\Yii::$app-&gt;ComponentID</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Please read the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-application-components.html">Application Components</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>section for details.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$controllerMap-detail">controllerMap</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="controllerMap"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property allows you to map a controller ID to an arbitrary controller class. By default, Yii maps controller IDs to controller classes based on a<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#controllerNamespace">convention</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>(e.g. the ID<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">post</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>would be mapped to<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">app\controllers\PostController</code>). By configuring this property, you can break the convention for specific controllers. In the following example,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">account</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>will be mapped to<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">app\controllers\UserController</code>, while<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">article</code>will be mapped to<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">app\controllers\PostController</code>.</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'controllerMap'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'account'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\controllers\UserController'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'article'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'class'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\controllers\PostController'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'enableCsrfValidation'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">false</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The array keys of this property represent the controller IDs, while the array values represent the corresponding controller class names or<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html">configurations</a>.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$controllerNamespace-detail">controllerNamespace</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="controllerNamespace"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the default namespace under which controller classes should be located. It defaults to<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">app\controllers</code>. If a controller ID is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">post</code>, by convention the corresponding controller class name (without namespace) would be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">PostController</code>, and the fully qualified class name would be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">app\controllers\PostController</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Controller classes may also be located under sub-directories of the directory corresponding to this namespace. For example, given a controller ID<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">admin/post</code>, the corresponding fully qualified controller class would be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">app\controllers\admin\PostController</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">It is important that the fully qualified controller classes should be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-autoloading.html">autoloadable</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and the actual namespace of your controller classes match the value of this property. Otherwise, you will receive "Page Not Found" error when accessing the application.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">In case you want to break the convention as described above, you may configure the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#controllerMap">controllerMap</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$language-detail">language</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="language"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the language in which the application should display content to end users. The default value of this property is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">en</code>, meaning English. You should configure this property if your application needs to support multiple languages.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The value of this property determines various<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-tutorial-i18n.html">internationalization</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>aspects, including message translation, date formatting, number formatting, etc. For example, the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-jui-datepicker.html">yii\jui\DatePicker</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>widget will use this property value by default to determine in which language the calendar should be displayed and how should the date be formatted.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">It is recommended that you specify a language in terms of an<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IETF_language_tag">IETF language tag</a>. For example,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">en</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>stands for English, while<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">en-US</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>stands for English (United States).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">More details about this property can be found in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-tutorial-i18n.html">Internationalization</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>section.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$modules-detail">modules</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="modules"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-modules.html">modules</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>that the application contains.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The property takes an array of module classes or<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html">configurations</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>with the array keys being the module IDs. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'modules'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;a&nbsp;"booking"&nbsp;module&nbsp;specified&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;module&nbsp;class<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'booking'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\modules\booking\BookingModule'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;a&nbsp;"comment"&nbsp;module&nbsp;specified&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;configuration&nbsp;array<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'comment'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'class'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\modules\comment\CommentModule'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'db'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'db'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Please refer to the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-modules.html">Modules</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>section for more details.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$name-detail">name</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="name"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the application name that may be displayed to end users. Unlike the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$id-detail">id</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property which should take a unique value, the value of this property is mainly for display purpose and does not need to be unique.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You do not always need to configure this property if none of your code is using it.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$params-detail">params</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="params"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies an array of globally accessible application parameters. Instead of using hardcoded numbers and strings everywhere in your code, it is a good practice to define them as application parameters in a single place and use the parameters in places where needed. For example, you may define the thumbnail image size as a parameter like the following:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'params'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'thumbnail.size'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">128</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">128</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Then in your code where you need to use the size value, you can simply use the code like the following:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$size&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">params</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'thumbnail.size'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">];<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$width&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">params</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'thumbnail.size'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">][</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">0</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">];</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Later if you decide to change the thumbnail size, you only need to modify it in the application configuration without touching any dependent code.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$sourceLanguage-detail">sourceLanguage</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="sourceLanguage"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the language that the application code is written in. The default value is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">'en-US'</code>, meaning English (United States). You should configure this property if the text content in your code is not in English.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Like the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#language">language</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property, you should configure this property in terms of an<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IETF_language_tag">IETF language tag</a>. For example,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">en</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>stands for English, while<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">en-US</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>stands for English (United States).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">More details about this property can be found in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-tutorial-i18n.html">Internationalization</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>section.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$timeZone-detail">timeZone</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="timeZone"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property is provided as an alternative way of setting the default time zone of PHP runtime. By configuring this property, you are essentially calling the PHP function<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://php.net/manual/en/function.date-default-timezone-set.php">date_default_timezone_set()</a>. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'timeZone'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'America/Los_Angeles'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$version-detail">version</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="version"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the version of the application. It defaults to<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">'1.0'</code>. You do not always need to configure this property if none of your code is using it.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Useful Properties<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="useful-properties"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The properties described in this subsection are not commonly configured because their default values stipulate common conventions. However, you may still configure them in case you want to break the conventions.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$charset-detail">charset</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="charset"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the charset that the application uses. The default value is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">'UTF-8'</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>which should be kept as is for most applications unless you are working with some legacy systems that use a lot of non-unicode data.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$defaultRoute-detail">defaultRoute</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="defaultRoute"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-runtime-routing.html">route</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>that an application should use when a request does not specify one. The route may consist of child module ID, controller ID, and/or action ID. For example,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">help</code>,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">post/create</code>,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">admin/post/create</code>. If action ID is not given, it will take the default value as specified in<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-controller.html#$defaultAction-detail">yii\base\Controller::$defaultAction</a>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">For<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-web-application.html">Web applications</a>, the default value of this property is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">'site'</code>, which means the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">SiteController</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>controller and its default action should be used. As a result, if you access the application without specifying a route, it will show the result of<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">app\controllers\SiteController::actionIndex()</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">For<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-console-application.html">console applications</a>, the default value is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">'help'</code>, which means the core command<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-console-controllers-helpcontroller.html#actionIndex()-detail">yii\console\controllers\HelpController::actionIndex()</a>should be used. As a result, if you run the command<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">yii</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>without providing any arguments, it will display the help information.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$extensions-detail">extensions</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="extensions"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the list of<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-extensions.html">extensions</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>that are installed and used by the application. By default, it will take the array returned by the file<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@vendor/yiisoft/extensions.php</code>. The<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">extensions.php</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>file is generated and maintained automatically when you use<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://getcomposer.org/">Composer</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to install extensions. So in most cases, you do not need to configure this property.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">In the special case when you want to maintain extensions manually, you may configure this property like the following:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'extensions'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'name'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'extension&nbsp;name'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'version'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'version&nbsp;number'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'bootstrap'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'BootstrapClassName'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;optional,&nbsp;may&nbsp;also&nbsp;be&nbsp;a&nbsp;configuration&nbsp;array<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'alias'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;optional<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'@alias1'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'to/path1'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'@alias2'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'to/path2'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;...&nbsp;more&nbsp;extensions&nbsp;like&nbsp;the&nbsp;above&nbsp;...<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">As you can see, the property takes an array of extension specifications. Each extension is specified with an array consisting of<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">name</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">version</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>elements. If an extension needs to run during the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-runtime-bootstrapping.html">bootstrap</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>process, a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">bootstrap</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>element may be specified with a bootstrapping class name or a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html">configuration</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>array. An extension may also define a few<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-aliases.html">aliases</a>.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$layout-detail">layout</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="layout"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the name of the default layout that should be used when rendering a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-views.html">view</a>. The default value is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">'main'</code>, meaning the layout file<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">main.php</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>under the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#layoutPath">layout path</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>should be used. If both of the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#layoutPath">layout path</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#viewPath">view path</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>are taking the default values, the default layout file can be represented as the path alias<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@app/views/layouts/main.php</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You may configure this property to be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">false</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>if you want to disable layout by default, although this is very rare.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$layoutPath-detail">layoutPath</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="layoutPath"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the path where layout files should be looked for. The default value is the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">layouts</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>sub-directory under the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#viewPath">view path</a>. If the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#viewPath">view path</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>is taking its default value, the default layout path can be represented as the path alias<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@app/views/layouts</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You may configure it as a directory or a path<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-aliases.html">alias</a>.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$runtimePath-detail">runtimePath</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="runtimePath"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the path where temporary files, such as log files, cache files, can be generated. The default value is the directory represented by the alias<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@app/runtime</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You may configure it as a directory or a path<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-aliases.html">alias</a>. Note that the runtime path must be writable by the process running the application. And the path should be protected from being accessed by end users because the temporary files under it may contain sensitive information.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">To simplify accessing to this path, Yii has predefined a path alias named<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@runtime</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>for it.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$viewPath-detail">viewPath</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="viewPath"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the root directory where view files are located. The default value is the directory represented by the alias<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@app/views</code>. You may configure it as a directory or a path<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-aliases.html">alias</a>.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$vendorPath-detail">vendorPath</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="vendorPath"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property specifies the vendor directory managed by<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://getcomposer.org/">Composer</a>. It contains all third party libraries used by your application, including the Yii framework. The default value is the directory represented by the alias<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@app/vendor</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You may configure this property as a directory or a path<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-aliases.html">alias</a>. When you modify this property, make sure you also adjust the Composer configuration accordingly.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">To simplify accessing to this path, Yii has predefined a path alias named<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">@vendor</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>for it.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-console-application.html#$enableCoreCommands-detail">enableCoreCommands</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="enableCoreCommands"></a></h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This property is supported by<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-console-application.html">console applications</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>only. It specifies whether the core commands included in the Yii release should be enabled. The default value is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">true</code>.</p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 30px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Application Events<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="application-events"></a></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">An application triggers several events during the lifecycle of handling an request. You may attach event handlers to these events in application configurations like the following,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'on&nbsp;beforeRequest'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;function&nbsp;(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$event</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">)&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;...<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">},<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The use of the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">on eventName</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>syntax is described in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html#configuration-format">Configurations</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>section.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Alternatively, you may attach event handlers during the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-runtime-bootstrapping.html">bootstrapping process</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>process after the application instance is created. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">on</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">(\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">base</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Application</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">EVENT_BEFORE_REQUEST</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,&nbsp;function&nbsp;(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$event</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">)&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;...<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">});</span></code></pre>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#EVENT_BEFORE_REQUEST-detail">EVENT_BEFORE_REQUEST</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="beforeRequest"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This event is triggered<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">before</em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>an application handles a request. The actual event name is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">beforeRequest</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">When this event is triggered, the application instance has been configured and initialized. So it is a good place to insert your custom code via the event mechanism to intercept the request handling process. For example, in the event handler, you may dynamically set the<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$language-detail">yii\base\Application::$language</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property based on some parameters.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#EVENT_BEFORE_REQUEST-detail">EVENT_AFTER_REQUEST</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="afterRequest"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This event is triggered<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">after</em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>an application finishes handling a request but<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">before</em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>sending the response. The actual event name is<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">afterRequest</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">When this event is triggered, the request handling is completed and you may take this chance to do some postprocessing of the request or customize the response.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Note that the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-web-response.html">response</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>component also triggers some events while it is sending out response content to end users. Those events are triggered<em style="box-sizing: border-box;">after</em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>this event.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#EVENT_BEFORE_REQUEST-detail">EVENT_BEFORE_ACTION</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="beforeAction"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This event is triggered<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">before</em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>running every<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html">controller action</a>. The actual event name is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">beforeAction</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The event parameter is an instance of<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-actionevent.html">yii\base\ActionEvent</a>. An event handler may set the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-actionevent.html#$isValid-detail">yii\base\ActionEvent::$isValid</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property to be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">false</code>to stop running the action. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'on&nbsp;beforeAction'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;function&nbsp;(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$event</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">)&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">some&nbsp;condition</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">)&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$event</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">isValid&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">false</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Note that the same<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">beforeAction</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>event is also triggered by<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-modules.html">modules</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html">controllers</a>. Application objects are the first ones triggering this event, followed by modules (if any), and finally controllers. If an event handler sets<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-actionevent.html#$isValid-detail">yii\base\ActionEvent::$isValid</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">false</code>, all the following events will NOT be triggered.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#EVENT_BEFORE_REQUEST-detail">EVENT_AFTER_ACTION</a><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="afterAction"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">This event is triggered<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">after</em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>running every<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html">controller action</a>. The actual event name is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">afterAction</code>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The event parameter is an instance of<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-actionevent.html">yii\base\ActionEvent</a>. Through the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-actionevent.html#$result-detail">yii\base\ActionEvent::$result</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property, an event handler may access or modify the action result. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'on&nbsp;afterAction'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;function&nbsp;(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$event</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">)&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">some&nbsp;condition</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">)&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;modify&nbsp;$event-&gt;result<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Note that the same<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">afterAction</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>event is also triggered by<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-modules.html">modules</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html">controllers</a>. These objects trigger this event in the reverse order as for that of<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">beforeAction</code>. That is, controllers are the first objects triggering this event, followed by modules (if any), and finally applications.</p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 30px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Application Lifecycle<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="application-lifecycle"></a></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">When an<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-entry-scripts.html">entry script</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>is being executed to handle a request, an application will undergo the following lifecycle:</p>
<ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">The entry script loads the application configuration as an array.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">The entry script creates a new instance of the application:
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#preInit()-detail">preInit()</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>is called, which configures some high priority application properties, such as<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$basePath-detail">basePath</a>.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">Register the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$errorHandler-detail">error handler</a>.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">Configure application properties.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#init()-detail">init()</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>is called which further calls<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#bootstrap()-detail">bootstrap()</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to run bootstrapping components.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">The entry script calls<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#run()-detail">yii\base\Application::run()</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to run the application:
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">Trigger the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#EVENT_BEFORE_REQUEST-detail">EVENT_BEFORE_REQUEST</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>event.</li>
<li style="box-sizing: border-box;">Handle the request: resolve the request into a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-runtime-routing.html">route</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and the associated parameters; create the module, controller and action objects as specified by the route; and run the action.</li>
